label: clads2-1
description: Under these values, ClaDS2 degenerates into CRBD.
ppl:
var tree = phyjs.bisse_32
	var particles = 5000
	var MAX_LAMBDA = 5
	var MAX_DIV = 5
	var MIN_LAMBDA = 0.00001
	var PANDA = false
var model = function()
{
	var sigma = 1e-7
	var alpha = 1
	var epsilon = 0
	var lambda_0 = 0.05
	var rho = 1
	var ret = simClaDS2( tree, lambda_0, alpha, sigma, epsilon, rho )
	var max_M = 10000
	var M = M_clads2GoesUndetected( tree.age, lambda_0, alpha, sigma, epsilon, rho, max_M)
	factor(Math.log(M))
	return ret
}
var dist = Infer({method: 'SMC', particles: particles, model: model})
dist.normalizationConstant
